Industries Inc","details":"This module serves as the core governance system that manages proposals and executes transactions through a Gnosis Safe. It acts as a modular controller, enabling flexible governance with support for various voting strategies and token standards. Key features: - Proposal submission with customizable proposer adapters - Flexible voting through a delegated strategy contract - Timelock mechanism for security - Execution period constraints - Safe integration for transaction execution The module delegates voting logic to a Strategy contract, allowing DAOs to customize their voting mechanisms without modifying the core governance module. Integration requirements: - Must be enabled as a module on the target Safe - Requires a valid Strategy contract for voting - Supports various proposer adapters for access
